...minta Biro Makanan mengantarkan
camilan malam.

127
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,320
Hanya tersisa keladi matang ini.

128
00:09:41,599 --> 00:09:43,799
Talas bagus di Tiongkok
tidak hanya talas pinang.

129
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,000
